{"title":"永丰屯新民歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永丰屯新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月好春光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月好春光，大家植树忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宅边种果木，榆树栽道旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井上葡萄架，河边柳絮扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过上三五年，绿荫盖村庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"午间能歇晌，夜晚好乘凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季鲜花遍，春秋果子黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美家乡好！歌声响四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六里屯街头诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯也亮来心也亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤油点灯灯花亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有文化心头亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤油灯下学文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯也亮来心也亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六里屯街头诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜出勤当两年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天我催太阳起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮困了我不眠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年三百六十日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜出勤当两年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六里屯街头诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱社妇女武艺高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓喧天红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱社妇女武艺高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘组成突击队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹个个逞英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打冲锋，头一炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐得主任哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得小伙蹦三尺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得懒汉不敢瞧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（张洪宾）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人不做睁眼瞎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑马要骑高头马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人不做睁眼瞎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不识字两眼黑麻麻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学了文化有办法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化就是无价宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有文化才能管理国家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（张福）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大跃进小唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（莲花落调）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大跃进，搞的欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心中好喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看我年老更能干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要和小伙子们比比看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耠稻地，插稻苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样活茬咱抢先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（曙光社老头合唱队）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}